description	"Sith Apprentice

^2Weaponry:

- Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Red Styles
-- Saber Defense (2)
-- Gun Defense   (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (1)
- Speed (1)
- Grip  (1)

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)
- Reinforcements (2)

A Sith apprentice was an individual that began serious training under a Sith Master, usually chosen by the Master him or herself, after the potential apprentice displayed an impressive act of loyalty or cruelty."